### Name for the cannabis plant

This article is about the Hindustani word. For other uses, see [Ganja (disambiguation)](/Ganja_(disambiguation)).

The word [ganja](/Ganja_(word)) inscribed, like a scar on the urban landscape, in graffiti in [Seville](/Seville), [Spain](/Spain). It’s a mark left behind, a whisper of something illicit, something that persists.

